---
import SectionWrapper from '../layouts/SectionWrapper.astro';
---

<SectionWrapper
  class="services-on-offer"
  itemscope
  itemtype="http://schema.org/Service"
>
  <div class="services-title-left">
    <h3 itemprop="name">SERVICES WE OFFER</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="services-right">
    <div
      class="service"
      itemprop="hasOfferCatalog"
      itemscope
      itemtype="http://schema.org/OfferCatalog"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/icon-1.svg"
        alt="Website Design Icon"
      />
      <h4 itemprop="name">Website Design:</h4>
      <p itemprop="description">
        Our website design service is centered around creating visually
        appealing and user-friendly websites that perfectly reflect your brand's
        identity. We focus on clean, aesthetic layouts that engage visitors and
        convey your message clearly, ensuring that even the smallest websites
        make a big impact.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="service"
      itemprop="hasOfferCatalog"
      itemscope
      itemtype="http://schema.org/OfferCatalog"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/icon-2.svg"
        alt="Website Development Icon"
      />
      <h4 itemprop="name">Website Development:</h4>
      <p itemprop="description">
        We bring designs to life with our website development service, ensuring
        a smooth, functional, and reliable online presence. Specializing in
        static websites, we provide fast-loading pages and a seamless user
        experience, ideal for small businesses looking to establish a solid
        digital footprint without the need for complex functionalities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="service"
      itemprop="hasOfferCatalog"
      itemscope
      itemtype="http://schema.org/OfferCatalog"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/icon-3.svg"
        alt="E-Commerce Solutions Icon"
      />
      <h4 itemprop="name">Small Business Focus:</h4>
      <p itemprop="description">
        Our services are specially tailored for small businesses aiming to make
        a significant online statement. We understand the unique challenges and
        opportunities small businesses face and offer personalized solutions
        that cater to your specific needs, ensuring your website serves as a
        powerful tool for growth and engagement.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="service"
      itemprop="hasOfferCatalog"
      itemscope
      itemtype="http://schema.org/OfferCatalog"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/icon-4.svg"
        alt="Responsive Web Design Icon"
      />
      <h4 itemprop="name">Responsive Web Design:</h4>
      <p itemprop="description">
        With a mobile-first approach, we ensure your website looks great and
        functions flawlessly across all devices, from desktop to mobile.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  .services-on-offer {
    background-image: url('/images/vector9.png'), url('/images/vector5.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat, no-repeat;
    background-position:
      left bottom,
      right top 20%;
    background-size: 15%, 5%;
  }
  h4 {
    font-family: var(--primary-font);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .service p {
    font-family: var(--primary-font);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.35rem;
  }

  .services-on-offer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 2rem 8rem;
  }

  .services-right {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    grid-row-gap: 3rem;
    grid-column-gap: 5rem;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-on-offer {
      padding: 2rem 2rem;
      background-image: url('/images/vector9.png');
      background-size: 50%;
      background-position: left bottom 15%;
    }

    .services-title-left {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .services-right {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    h4 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
